title: About Me
text:
I am a second year PhD student studying Nutritional Sciences at University of New Hampshire.


I hope to pursue a career in research, specifically focusing on nutrition epidemiology and data science.



B.S. Nutrition and Dietetics, Drexel University, 2020
M.S. Nutrition and Metabolism, Boston University, 2023
Ph.D. Nutritional Sciences, University of New Hampshire, Anticipated Graduation 2027
